<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - QR Menu</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cairo:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');

        * {
            font-family: 'Cairo', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            z-index: 10;
            position: relative;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: 150px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .error-description {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-404 {
            padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .btn-primary-404 {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .btn-primary-404:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            color: #764ba2;
        }

        .btn-outline-404 {
            background: transparent;
            color: white;
            border: 2px solid white;
        }

        .btn-outline-404:hover {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            50% {
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }
        }

        .bg-shapes {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .shape {
            position: absolute;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .shape-1 {
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            top: 10%;
            left: 10%;
            animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .shape-2 {
            width: 150px;
            height: 150px;
            bottom: 20%;
            right: 15%;
            animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
        }

        .shape-3 {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            top: 50%;
            right: 30%;
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .developer-footer {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            color: white;
            opacity: 0.8;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .developer-footer a {
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .error-code {
                font-size: 100px;
            }

            .error-message {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .error-description {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg-shapes">
    <div class="shape shape-1"></div>
    <div class="shape shape-2"></div>
    <div class="shape shape-3"></div>
</div>

<div class="error-container">
    <div class="error-code">404</div>
    <h1 class="error-message">الصفحة غير موجودة!</h1>
    <p class="error-description">
        عذراً، لم نتمكن من العثور على الصفحة التي تبحث عنها
    </p>
    <div class="error-actions">
        <a href="/" class="btn-404 btn-primary-404">
            <i class="bi bi-house"></i>
            الصفحة الرئيسية
        </a>
        <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn-404 btn-outline-404">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
            رجوع
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="developer-footer">
    Developed by
    <a href="https://www.olosolutions.cc/" target="_blank">Olosolutions</a>
</div>
</body>
</html>